  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1826450/extras/7bc85c6f2b96e74a25c9822d27aef29d.avif?t=1768360559\" width=576 height=300 /></span><br>◆Raise up idols by idling!<br>The basis of the game rule is Idling!<br>Idols grow up over time.<br>Time resource management simulation.<br><br>① Let's decide the name of the idol group!<br>② Let's choose an idol at the audition!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1826450/extras/3b86822c737bd1efc398db60bc92229a.poster.avif?t=1768360559\" width=512 height=288 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1826450/extras/3b86822c737bd1efc398db60bc92229a.webm?t=1768360559\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1826450/extras/3b86822c737bd1efc398db60bc92229a.mp4?t=1768360559\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>③ Start training and work with the whole group!<br>Collect fans and earn money.<br>When an event occurs, the idol's ability will increase.<br>And it is also important to take a rest when idls are tired!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1826450/extras/e6be2f92cbf52dd13d280882839a7004.poster.avif?t=1768360559\" width=512 height=288 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1826450/extras/e6be2f92cbf52dd13d280882839a7004.webm?t=1768360559\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1826450/extras/e6be2f92cbf52dd13d280882839a7004.mp4?t=1768360559\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>④ Use the money you earn to buy health recovery items and strengthen your training facilities.<br>A fulfilling training environment is indispensable for raising top idols!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1826450/extras/d6d50df0e51d55a32cc52d6259b0e997.poster.avif?t=1768360559\" width=512 height=288 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1826450/extras/d6d50df0e51d55a32cc52d6259b0e997.webm?t=1768360559\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1826450/extras/d6d50df0e51d55a32cc52d6259b0e997.mp4?t=1768360559\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>⑤ A live concert will be held when the funds are saved!<br>The way customers enter depends on the number of fans in the entire group.<br>Let's aim to hold the idol's dream, \"Dome Live\"!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1826450/extras/13b48b15c582c3998cce3d739dc71d78.poster.avif?t=1768360559\" width=512 height=288 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1826450/extras/13b48b15c582c3998cce3d739dc71d78.webm?t=1768360559\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1826450/extras/13b48b15c582c3998cce3d739dc71d78.mp4?t=1768360559\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>⑥ Training is completed in 4 seasons of spring, summer, autumn and winter, and 1 year of activity!<br>The idol rank is determined by the funds earned by the group!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1826450/extras/6d02a31d8ce03ad37bb326634b9cec03.poster.avif?t=1768360559\" width=512 height=288 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1826450/extras/6d02a31d8ce03ad37bb326634b9cec03.webm?t=1768360559\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1826450/extras/6d02a31d8ce03ad37bb326634b9cec03.mp4?t=1768360559\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>⑦ And to the next training ...!<br>There is no end to idol group development!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1826450/extras/e099eac5d2fcd2af3ecac3f08d3aaf10.poster.avif?t=1768360559\" width=512 height=288 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1826450/extras/e099eac5d2fcd2af3ecac3f08d3aaf10.webm?t=1768360559\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1826450/extras/e099eac5d2fcd2af3ecac3f08d3aaf10.mp4?t=1768360559\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>◆The one and only idols<br>Idols have random names, appearances, stats, and personalities.<br>It is automatically generated by AI during the audition.<br>Is the criterion for selecting members of the group your favorite appearance or ability score?<br>Choose the one and only idol and raise it to become a top idol!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1826450/extras/64028d56a0cb5ce8234248b3fbb5bb19.avif?t=1768360559\" width=480 height=192 /></span><br><br>◆Gameplay where the same thing never happens again<br>Depending on the random element, you can enjoy different developments each time you play.<br>・ All idol appearances and stats are random<br>・ Randomly generate advantageous training effects for each season<br>・ Events that fluctuate idol stats and physical strength occur randomly<br><br>There is no absolute answer for idol training.<br>As a producer, always be flexible!<br><br>◆language<br>Supports Japanese and English<br>You can switch from the config button on the title page.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1826450/extras/2b71604e307b1b4191c86eb0c90181c0.avif?t=1768360559\" width=512 height=288 /></span>",
